cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.CV 

This paper is primarily focused on the design and implementation of a scalable production system for Federated Learning, which is a subfield of Machine Learning (ML). Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the challenges and solutions related to distributed computing, system design, and data management, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of Federated Learning in the domain of mobile devices, which could be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
